INSTALL

To run webLETS you will need;
1. a directory on a webserver running PHP and MySQL
2. a MySQL database, and at least one user with table modification priviledges.

To install webLETS:
1.  untar the package in the directory you wish the system to reside (This must be under your server's Document Root)
2.  set the permissions on the directory for global read/write access (chmod 777 your-directory)
3.  point your web browser to install.php, and follow the directions.

